# Normalize line endings: LF in the repository and in the working tree.
# Go tooling (gofmt) always writes LF, and CI runs on Linux, so pinning eol=lf
# keeps the working tree consistent on Windows checkouts and avoids spurious
# CRLF/LF diffs (e.g. after the gofmt PostToolUse hook).
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicit binaries (never normalize).
*.exe binary
*.png binary
*.db binary
